{"title":"為了能找到想要的內容 好用的搜尋相關參數","slug":"search-engine-operators","html":"<h2 id=\"google\">Google</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://support.google.com/websearch/answer/2466433\">Refine web searches - Google Search Help</a></li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>關鍵字</th>\n<th>功能</th>\n<th>範例</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>OR</code>／<code> |</code></td>\n<td>內容包含其一關鍵字</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.google.com/search?&amp;q=Gundam+OR+Evangelion\">Gundam OR Evangelion</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>AND</code></td>\n<td>內容包含所有關鍵字</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.google.com/search?&amp;q=Gundam+AND+Evangelion\">Gundam AND Evangelion</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>-</code></td>\n<td>內容不包含該關鍵字</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.google.com/search?&amp;q=Gundam+-Unicorn\">Gundam -Unicorn</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>*</code></td>\n<td>任意字元補足關鍵字缺失部份</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=steve+*+apple\">steve * apple</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>()</code></td>\n<td>指定特定關鍵字條件</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%28ipad+OR+iphone%29+apple\">(ipad OR iphone) apple</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&quot;&quot;</code></td>\n<td>內容完全符合指定關鍵字</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>$</code></td>\n<td>搜尋價錢</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=ipad+%24329\">ipad $329</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>#..#</code></td>\n<td>搜尋兩者之間範圍的內容</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E3%82%B2%E3%83%BC%E3%83%A0+1990..1999\">ゲーム 1990..1999</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>before:</code>／<code>after:</code></td>\n<td>搜尋特定時間範圍的內容</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E5%8D%83%E3%81%A8%E5%8D%83%E5%